---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout 
  title="AsistanApp – Çok Kanallı AI Asistan Platformu" 
  description="İşletmeniz için WhatsApp, Instagram, Facebook, Twitter/X, Web ve Ses kanallarında yapay zekâ destekli müşteri iletişimi. KVKV/GDPR uyumlu, üretime hazır."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero section-lg">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content text-center">
        <div class="chip animate-scale-in">
          <span data-i18n="tr">🤖 7/24 Akıllı Asistan • Otomatik Satış • Randevu Yönetimi</span>
          <span data-i18n="en">🤖 24/7 Smart Assistant • Automated Sales • Appointment Management</span>
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="hero-title gradient-text animate-fade-in-up">
          <span data-i18n="tr">Yapay Zeka Müşterilerinizle Konuşsun</span>
          <span data-i18n="en">Let AI Talk to Your Customers</span>
        </h1>
        
        <p class="hero-description animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s; opacity: 0;">
          <span data-i18n="tr">
            AsistanApp, işletmenizin müşterileriyle WhatsApp, Instagram, Facebook, Web ve Ses kanallarında 
            7/24 akıllı konuşmalar yapmasını sağlar. Yapay zeka asistanınız müşteri sorularını yanıtlar, 
            ürün satar ve randevu alır - siz uyurken bile.
          </span>
          <span data-i18n="en">
            AsistanApp enables your business to have intelligent 24/7 conversations with customers across 
            WhatsApp, Instagram, Facebook, Web, and Voice channels. Your AI assistant answers questions, 
            sells products, and books appointments - even while you sleep.
          </span>
        </p>
        
        <div class="hero-cta animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.4s; opacity: 0;">
          <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg hover-glow hover-bounce" href="/pre-register">
            <span data-i18n="tr">🎯 Hemen Ön Kayıt Olun</span>
            <span data-i18n="en">🎯 Join the Waitlist Now</span>
          </a>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg hover-scale" href="/features">
            <span data-i18n="tr">✨ Özellikleri Keşfedin</span>
            <span data-i18n="en">✨ Discover Features</span>
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="hero-badges animate-fade-in-up animate-stagger" style="animation-delay: 0.6s;">
          <span class="badge animate-float" style="animation-delay: 0s;">%99.9 Uptime</span>
          <span class="badge animate-float" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">RAG + Voice</span>
          <span class="badge animate-float" style="animation-delay: 1s;">KVKK/GDPR</span>
          <span class="badge animate-float" style="animation-delay: 1.5s;">1M+ Scalable</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features Section -->
  <section class="features-section section observe-animation" style="background: var(--bg-accent);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center animate-fade-in-up">
        <span data-i18n="tr">Neden AsistanApp'i Seçmelisiniz?</span>
        <span data-i18n="en">Why Choose AsistanApp?</span>
      </h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-3 animate-stagger">
        <div class="card hover-lift animate-fade-in-up">
          <div class="feature-icon animate-float">🤖</div>
          <h3>
            <span data-i18n="tr">Müşterilerle Doğal Konuşma</span>
            <span data-i18n="en">Natural Customer Conversations</span>
          </h3>
          <p>
            <span data-i18n="tr">
              Yapay zeka asistanınız müşterilerinizle tıpkı bir insan gibi konuşur. 
              Ürün önerilerinden teknik desteğe, her soruya akıllı ve kişiselleştirilmiş yanıtlar verir.
            </span>
            <span data-i18n="en">
              Your AI assistant talks to customers just like a human would. 
              From product recommendations to technical support, it provides smart and personalized answers to every question.
            </span>
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card hover-lift animate-fade-in-up">
          <div class="feature-icon animate-float" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">📱</div>
          <h3>
            <span data-i18n="tr">Her Kanalda Aynı Zeka</span>
            <span data-i18n="en">Same Intelligence, Every Channel</span>
          </h3>
          <p>
            <span data-i18n="tr">
              Müşteriniz WhatsApp'tan mı, Instagram'dan mı, telefonla mı arayacak? 
              Farketmez! Yapay zeka asistanınız her kanalda aynı kalitede hizmet verir.
            </span>
            <span data-i18n="en">
              Whether your customer contacts via WhatsApp, Instagram, or phone call - 
              it doesn't matter! Your AI assistant provides the same quality service across all channels.
            </span>
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card hover-lift animate-fade-in-up">
          <div class="feature-icon animate-float" style="animation-delay: 1s;">🎤</div>
          <h3>
            <span data-i18n="tr">Telefonla da Konuşur</span>
            <span data-i18n="en">Talks on Phone Too</span>
          </h3>
          <p>
            <span data-i18n="tr">
              Yapay zeka asistanınız sadece yazışmakla kalmaz, müşterilerinizle telefonda da 
              gerçek bir insan gibi konuşur. Sesli sipariş alır, randevu planlar.
            </span>
            <span data-i18n="en">
              Your AI assistant doesn't just text - it also talks on the phone like a real human. 
              Takes voice orders, schedules appointments.
            </span>
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card hover-lift animate-fade-in-up">
          <div class="feature-icon animate-float" style="animation-delay: 1.5s;">🔍</div>
          <h3>
            <span data-i18n="tr">Şirketinizi Tanır</span>
            <span data-i18n="en">Knows Your Business</span>
          </h3>
          <p>
            <span data-i18n="tr">
              Yapay zeka asistanınız şirketinizin ürünlerini, fiyatlarını, politikalarını bilir. 
              Müşteri sorularına şirketinizin verilerinden doğru yanıtlar verir.
            </span>
            <span data-i18n="en">
              Your AI assistant knows your company's products, prices, and policies. 
              It provides accurate answers to customer questions using your business data.
            </span>
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card hover-lift animate-fade-in-up">
          <div class="feature-icon animate-float" style="animation-delay: 2s;">🔒</div>
          <h3>
            <span data-i18n="tr">Güvenli ve Gizli</span>
            <span data-i18n="en">Secure & Private</span>
          </h3>
          <p>
            <span data-i18n="tr">
              Müşteri verileriniz tamamen güvende. KVKK ve GDPR uyumlu sistem, 
              hiçbir müşteri bilgisini paylaşmaz veya kötüye kullanmaz.
            </span>
            <span data-i18n="en">
              Your customer data is completely secure. KVKK and GDPR compliant system 
              never shares or misuses any customer information.
            </span>
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card hover-lift animate-fade-in-up">
          <div class="feature-icon animate-float" style="animation-delay: 2.5s;">📈</div>
          <h3>
            <span data-i18n="tr">Hiç Durmaz, Büyür</span>
            <span data-i18n="en">Never Stops, Always Grows</span>
          </h3>
          <p>
            <span data-i18n="tr">
              Yapay zeka asistanınız 7/24 çalışır, hiç yorulmaz. İşiniz büyüdükçe 
              milyonlarca müşteriyle aynı anda konuşabilir.
            </span>
            <span data-i18n="en">
              Your AI assistant works 24/7, never gets tired. As your business grows, 
              it can talk to millions of customers simultaneously.
            </span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats Section -->
  <section class="stats-section section observe-animation" style="background: var(--primary); color: white;">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2 class="animate-fade-in-up" style="color: white; margin-bottom: var(--space-12);">
        <span data-i18n="tr">AsistanApp Rakamlarla</span>
        <span data-i18n="en">AsistanApp by the Numbers</span>
      </h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-4 animate-stagger">
        <div class="stat-item animate-scale-in hover-scale">
          <h3 class="stat-number animate-pulse">1M+</h3>
          <p class="stat-label">
            <span data-i18n="tr">Müşteri Kapasitesi</span>
            <span data-i18n="en">Customer Capacity</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="stat-item animate-scale-in hover-scale">
          <h3 class="stat-number animate-pulse">6+</h3>
          <p class="stat-label">
            <span data-i18n="tr">İletişim Kanalı</span>
            <span data-i18n="en">Communication Channels</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="stat-item animate-scale-in hover-scale">
          <h3 class="stat-number animate-pulse">%99.9</h3>
          <p class="stat-label">
            <span data-i18n="tr">Kesintisiz Çalışma</span>
            <span data-i18n="en">Uptime Guarantee</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="stat-item animate-scale-in hover-scale">
          <h3 class="stat-number animate-pulse">RLS</h3>
          <p class="stat-label">
            <span data-i18n="tr">Güvenli Veri İzolasyonu</span>
            <span data-i18n="en">Secure Data Isolation</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="cta-section section observe-animation" style="background: var(--bg-accent);">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2 class="animate-fade-in-up">
        <span data-i18n="tr">Müşteri Deneyiminizi Dönüştürmeye Hazır mısınız?</span>
        <span data-i18n="en">Ready to Transform Your Customer Experience?</span>
      </h2>
      
      <p class="animate-fade-in-up" style="font-size: var(--font-size-lg); margin-bottom: var(--space-8); animation-delay: 0.2s; opacity: 0;">
        <span data-i18n="tr">
          Yapay zeka asistanınız müşterilerinizle konuşmaya başlasın. 
          Bugün ön kayıt olun, lansmanımızda ilk kullananlardan birin.
        </span>
        <span data-i18n="en">
          Let your AI assistant start talking to your customers. 
          Register today and be among the first users at our launch.
        </span>
      </p>
      
      <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg hover-glow hover-bounce animate-scale-in" href="/pre-register" style="animation-delay: 0.4s; opacity: 0;">
        <span data-i18n="tr">🚀 Ücretsiz Ön Kayıt</span>
        <span data-i18n="en">🚀 Free Pre-Registration</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Hero Section */
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-primary) 0%, var(--bg-accent) 100%);
    padding: var(--space-24) 0;
  }
  
  .hero-content {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .hero-title {
    font-size: var(--font-size-5xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-extrabold);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-hover));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }
  
  .hero-description {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
  
  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }
  
  .hero-badges {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  
  /* Feature Section */
  .feature-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-hover));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }
  
  /* Stats Section */
  .stat-item {
    padding: var(--space-6);
  }
  
  .stat-number {
    font-size: var(--font-size-4xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-extrabold);
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }
  
  .stat-label {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium);
    margin: 0;
  }
  
  /* CTA Section */
  .cta-section {
    background: var(--bg-accent);
  }
  
  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      padding: var(--space-16) 0;
    }
    
    .hero-title {
      font-size: var(--font-size-3xl);
    }
    
    .hero-description {
      font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    }
    
    .hero-cta {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
    
    .hero-cta .btn {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 300px;
    }
    
    .hero-badges {
      gap: var(--space-2);
    }
  }
</style>